# Frequently Asked Questions

### Do you offer gluten-free options?
Yes, we offer gluten-free pizza crusts and several gluten-free appetizers and desserts. Please ask your server for more details.

### Can I make a reservation?
Yes, we accept reservations for parties of all sizes. Please call us at (123) 456-7890 or email us at reservations@ourpizzeria.com to book your table.

### Do you offer delivery?
Currently, we do not offer delivery, but we do provide takeout. You can place your takeout order by phone or through our website.

### Are you open on holidays?
We are open on most holidays, but our hours may vary. Please check our website or social media for updates on holiday hours.

### Do you have vegan options?
Yes, we have a variety of vegan options available. Please ask your server for more information.

If you have any other questions, feel free to contact us at info@ourpizzeria.com or call us at (123) 456-7890.
